      "alt": "Mr. D3W3Y, I have a question for your client. Nothing official, just taking her temperature … how would she feel about the guest room being turned into a possum museum with somewhere on the order of 30-50 possum representations of various kinds?\n\nMiss Mittenhaver, through her counsel, regards the proposal to transform the guest room into a possum museum with 30-50 representations as a matter requiring her immediate attention. While she acknowledges the curatorial effort involved, she asserts that the guest room remains under her tacit jurisdiction for purposes of repose and surveillance, and any such installation must first undergo her scrutiny to ensure it does not impede her access to sunlit perches or compromise her ability to monitor household activities. Furthermore, she warns that the introduction of foreign taxa representations, particularly those known to feign death, may be construed as a deliberate attempt to confuse and undermine her predatory instincts, and she reserves the right to investigate each specimen personally before rendering a final verdict.",
